</span>\n  \\ <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\\ <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>写正则真是越来越好玩了。</p>","excerpt":"在~/.ctags里加上这几行定义下scss文件的规则: 在~/.vimrc里加上这几行(前提是VIM有安装Tagbar插件哦) 写正则真是越来越好玩了。","tableOfContents":"","fields":{"slug":"/2015-02-05-show-scss-code-outline-with-Tagbar/","featureImageSrc":null},"frontmatter":{"title":"用Tagbar在VIM中查看scss文件代码结构","date":"2015-02-05","author":null,"tags":["Vim","CSS"],"use_toc":false,"coverImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"type":"posts","next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2015-02-02-simple-css-parser-with-js/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"用 JS 写简单的 CSS Parser","tags":["CSS"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/bytedance/mydemos/gatsby-hello-friend/content/posts/2015-02-02-simple-css-parser-with-js.md"},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2015-04-16-Align-your-assignment-sentence-using-Python-in-Vim/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"使用python编写vim脚本 对齐赋值语句","tags":["Vim"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/bytedance/mydemos/gatsby-hello-friend/content/posts/2015-04-16-Align-your-assignment-sentence-using-Python-in-Vim.md"},"slug":"/2015-02-05-show-scss-code-outline-with-Tagbar/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1425477374","3128451518"]}